<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">是甚麽로 方便삼아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="4">展轉이 擧覺면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="5">百千 方便 億萬 說話</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="6">이 고즤 쓸  업</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="7">語黙動靜 二邊上의</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="8">寸步間도 여읨 업시</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="9">惺惺不昧 擧覺되</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="10">이 무삼 道理런고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="11">드 者를 되드오면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="12">無去 無來 亦無住라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="13">取也不得 捨也不得</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="14">當處 現前 昭昭나</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="15">不在身內 不在身外</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="16">廓落太虛의 起淸風</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="17">相耶아 無相耶아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="18">行住坐臥 語黙動靜</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="19">念念不眛 是甚麽오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="20">行也坐也 同運며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="21">去也來也 여읨 업</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="22">前念 後念 頓斷고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="23">一念 現前 圓明道理</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="24">衆生 諸佛 增減 업</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1">歷千劫以不古고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="2">亘萬世而長今이란</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">이 말삼이 올오니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="4">自己上의 읻 寶物</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="5">나 알고 쓰거니와</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="6">남들도 알으신</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="7">眞實노 모로거든</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="8">語黙 中의 차자야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="9">나와 함 同行</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="10">이 寶貝를 어든 後</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="11">萬乘 七寶 불어 며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="12">萬塔 黃金 貴손가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="13">七寶 黃金 쓰라 들면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="14">盡 時節 읻거니와</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="15">自己上의 어든 寶物</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="16">암만 쓴들 盡손가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="17">呵呵 즐거올샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="18">樂耶아 不樂耶아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="19">樂不樂이 둘 아닐</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="20">이 무삼 妙理런고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="21">未證事란 일컨 마</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="22">格外丈夫 善君子</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="23">나의 말삼 들어보소</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="24">如是道의 滋味 붇쳐</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">速效心을 디 말며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">懶怠想도 쓰디 말고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="3">슬금 슬금 다듬아</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="4">밤도록 가 길의</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="5">도 들  아니 볼가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="6">今時 大覺 몯 일워도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="7">聖智種子 어더시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="8">凡地位에 드러셔도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="9">恒常 快樂 받오며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="10">聖地位에 올나셔도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="11">普濟群品 노댠니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="12">이러므로 三世佛이</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="13">依此修證 오시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="14">古今 歷代 祖師들도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="15">依此發慧 오시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="16">發信大智 菩薩들도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="17">依此度生 오시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="18">二乘聲聞 緣覺들도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="19">依此作福 오시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="20">乃至天下 老和尙도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="21">依此觀行 오시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="22">三道 受苦 衆生들도</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="23">依此야 報를 받</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="24">自己 寶物 알고 쓰면</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">苦中의도 樂人이요</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">自己 寶物 모로오면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">苦樂이 一揆니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="4">이러모로 衆生 諸佛</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="5">一理齊平다 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="6">理平은 올커니와</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="7">苦樂은 不平</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="8">有智丈夫 살피시소</sent><!-- title: 제목, title: 편명, main: 본문, anno: 협주-->
